==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Epidermic
<hw>Ep`i*der"mic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧pidermique</ets>.]</ety> <def>Epidermal; connected with the
skin or the bark.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Epidermic administration of medicine</b></col>
<fld>(Med.)</fld>, <cd>the application of medicine to the skin by
friction.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Epidermical</ent>⟦br⟧
